{
  "texts": [
    "This study was conducted with university students from three state universities in Turkey, and the scale's validity and applicability in different cultural contexts have not been explicitly examined.",
    "Therefore, the generalizability of the findings to different populations, such as individuals from various age groups, educational backgrounds, or cultural environments, may be limited.",
    "Future research should explore the scale's validity and applicability across diverse cultural settings and conduct additional psychometric analyses to enhance its reliability and validity.",
    "The scale items do not focus on any specific version of ChatGPT.",
    "Currently, we believe that the scale is applicable to all versions of ChatGPT."
  ]
}